  "prompt": "How can I know about Bhopal hotels?",
  "response": "To find information about hotels in Bhopal, you can use the following methods:\n\n1. **Online Travel Websites**:\n   - Visit popular travel websites such as **Booking.com**, **Agoda**, **Expedia**, **MakeMyTrip**, or **Goibibo**.\n   - Use filters to narrow down your search by price, location, ratings, and amenities.\n   - Read reviews from previous guests to get an idea of the hotel's quality.\n\n2. **Google Search**:\n   - Search for \"hotels in Bhopal\" on Google.\n   - Google will display a list of hotels with ratings, photos, and contact details. You can also view them on Google Maps.\n\n3. **Hotel Aggregator Apps**:\n   - Download apps like **OYO**, **FabHotels**, or **Treebo** to explore budget and mid-range options.\n\n4. **Social Media and Forums**:\n   - Check platforms TripAdvisor or Reddit for recommendations and honest reviews from travelers.\n\n5. **Direct Hotel Websites**:\n   - If you have a specific hotel in mind, visit their official website for detailed information, promotions, and direct booking options.\n\n6. **Travel Blogs and Guides**:\n   - Look for travel blogs or guides about Bhopal that include hotel recommendations.\n\n7. **Local Recommendations**:\n   - Ask friends or family who have visited Bhopal for their suggestions.\n\nKey areas to stay in Bhopal include **MP Nagar**, **Arera Colony**, **New Market**, and **Bairagarh**, as they are close to major attractions and have good connectivity.",
